<br>
         This is how he gained the name of “Demon of The Battlefield” for his unmatched rage and abilities in the thick of the battle. He has traveled to the Far East to receive training in the art of war. Surprisingly the code of the Samurai does not differ far from the code of honor some Vikings obey.        <br>
<br>
        His powers are rather pale in comparison to other immortals but he more than makes up for it in ability.. He has the power to heal at an amazing rate from almost any wound. His sword is said to be unbreakable because of its magical Runes, seeing it held up against a Titan. He also has the ability to communicate with some forms of animals. His fighting abilities are almost unmatched among those who have tested him. He has waged war for centuries and those who meet him on a battlefield under an opposing flag. God help them.<br>
